# Cushion Cut Diamond Earrings: Prices, Styles & What to Buy

Cushion cut diamond earrings start at [$325 for a lab-grown 1/4 ct tw pair in 14K white gold](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-4-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251842?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). Natural cushion diamond studs start at [$623 for 1/4 ct tw in 14K white gold](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-4-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251840?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational).

Before you buy, there are two things almost nobody tells you. First: "ct tw" means the total weight of both earrings combined — not per ear. Second: cushion studs need matched stones. Get both of those wrong and you'll regret the purchase.

This guide covers both — plus full price tables by carat, every metal option, and all the styles.

---

**TL;DR**

- **Cheapest lab cushion studs:** [$325 — 1/4 ct tw, 14K white gold, F-G/VS2-SI1](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-4-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251842?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)
- **Best everyday lab cushion studs:** [$1,380 — 1 ct tw (0.50ct per ear), 14K white gold](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251851?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)
- **Big lab cushion studs:** [$2,110 — 2 ct tw (1ct per ear), 14K white gold](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-2-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251857?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)
- **Natural cushion studs (on sale):** [$3,003 — 1 ct tw, 14K white gold, currently -30%](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-ct-tw-h-i-si1-si2-item-251849?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)
- **Halo cushion stud (50% off):** [$555 — 1/3 ct tw, 14K white gold](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-diamond-halo-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-3-ct-tw-item-201193?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)
- **Leverback halo cushion:** [$2,857 — 18K white gold, cushion center with diamond halo](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/diamond-halo-leverback-earrings-with-cushion-cut-diamonds-in-18k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-315862?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)

