The cushion shape works particularly well with a halo setting. The soft square outline of the cushion and the round halo of small diamonds complement each other — the contrast between the cushion's angular-ish silhouette and the round halo perimeter creates a layered look. It reads as more interesting than a round center with a round halo, which can look like a single large circle at earring distance.

