## Lab Grown Cushion Cut Diamond Earrings

Lab-grown cushion earrings are the main reason this market has grown so fast. The prices are accessible. The quality grades are high. And for earrings — where you're never looking at a grading certificate — lab vs natural is invisible to everyone around you.

The lab cushion stud range runs from [$325 (1/4 ct tw)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-4-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251842?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) to [$5,230 (6 ct tw)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-6-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-280410?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). F-G color and VS2-SI1 clarity throughout the range. That's good grade specs — well above the H-I/SI1-SI2 of the natural stud options.

Why do lab earrings have better grade specs than natural earrings at lower prices? Because lab-grown diamonds are produced in high quality consistently. Natural diamonds at H-I/SI1-SI2 are used in jewelry settings because they're eye-clean at earring size. Lab at F-G/VS2-SI1 are available cheaply enough to put in earring settings. The lab version wins on specs at every price point.

The sweet spots:
- Entry-level: [$890 for 1/2 ct tw](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-2-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251845?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) — 0.25ct per ear, real presence
- Everyday: [$1,380 for 1 ct tw](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251851?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) — 0.50ct per ear, the most popular size
- Statement: [$2,110 for 2 ct tw](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-2-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251857?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) — 1ct per ear, noticeable from across the room
- Show stopper: [$5,230 for 6 ct tw](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-6-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-280410?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) — 3ct per ear

