## Final Verdict — Best For

**Best first cushion earring:** [Lab 1 ct tw, 14K white gold — $1,380](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251851?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). Half a carat per ear. F-G color. VS2-SI1 clarity. The most popular size for a reason. Goes everywhere.

**Best budget pick:** [Halo cushion stud — $555 (50% off)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-diamond-halo-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-1-3-ct-tw-item-201193?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). More visual impact than a plain stud at this price. Halo adds size. Currently half price.

**Best statement lab stud:** [Lab 2 ct tw, 14K white gold — $2,110](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/cushion-cut-lab-grown-diamond-stud-earrings-in-14k-white-gold-2-ct-tw-f-g-vs2-si1-item-251857?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). One carat per ear. F-G/VS2-SI1. These get noticed. That's the point.

**Best for occasions and events:** [Leverback halo cushion — $2,857 (50% off)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/earrings/diamond-halo-leverback-earrings-with-cushion-cut-diamonds-in-18k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-315862?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational). 18K white gold. Secure closure. Cushion centers with halo. Earrings that move. Half off.

